sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Launcher as Java LauncherApp
    participant Screen as flint.ui.Screen
    participant AppManager as flint.app.AppManager
    participant Contract as MVP Native Launch Contract
    participant Registry as Native AppRegistry
    participant Permission as Native PermissionManager
    participant JVM as FlintJvmHost
    participant App as Java User/System App

    User->>Launcher: Touch / button select app
    Launcher->>Screen: render installed app list
    Launcher->>AppManager: listInstalledApps()
    AppManager-->>Launcher: AppInfo[]
    Launcher->>AppManager: launch(appId)
    AppManager->>Contract: native launch request

    Note over Contract,JVM: Implemented today as MVP contract; full dynamic app lifecycle is planned.
    Contract->>Registry: findById(appId)
    Registry-->>Contract: AppManifest / missing
    Contract->>Permission: check caller + requested permissions
    Permission-->>Contract: allowed / denied

    alt permission denied or manifest missing
        Contract-->>AppManager: false / error
        AppManager-->>Launcher: launch failed
        Launcher->>Screen: draw error state
    else permission allowed
        Contract->>JVM: launchSystemApp(mainClass)
        JVM->>JVM: launchProgram(FlintApp.jar)
        Note over JVM,App: Planned: load mainClass, instantiate FlintApp, call onStart(AppContext).
        JVM-->>AppManager: true / pending runtime result
        AppManager-->>Launcher: launch success
    end
